Description 	"Darth Sidious

Class: Sith.
Class Summary: 
An offensive force user with enhanced forcepool and powerful Dark Side abilities. 

Lightsaber
- Defense (2)
- Can use Cyan, Yellow and Red styles
- Special Spin DFA
- No increased BP Drain while in air
- Force Deflect (3)

Force Powers:
- Jump (3)
- Push (3)
- Pull (3)
- Lightning (3)
- Grip (3)
- Sense (3)
- Improved Saberthrow (3)
- Force Block (3)
- Force Focus (3)

Attributes:
- Immune to Force Sense
- Runs faster in Melee

Palpatine was the chancellor of the Republic during the Clone Wars and the consequent fall of the Republic. Little did anyone suspect how Palpatine had engineered his own rise to power. Hidden beneath a facade of wan smiles and smooth political speeches was a Sith Lord. In truth, Palpatine was well versed in the ways of the Force, having been apprentice to Darth Plagueis the Wise, a Sith Lord who was a master of the arcane."